oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dt4dkj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDt4dkj5.png&h=d03e935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月8日<br />\n星期日<br />\n到美國領事館(遊行路線待定) <br />\n<br />\n唱住美國國歌 (下面有MV歌詞) <br />\n全力支持通過<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n[全登集氣]推到民陣搞，9月8號星期日大遊行，援請通過香港人權法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531140</a><br />\n<br />\n美國人權及民主法案大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARgCLoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARgCLoO.jpg&h=045fa316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住練定美國國歌到時唱！！！！<br />\n </span></span><br />\n~~Oh, say can you see, <br />\nBy the dawn's early light, <br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed, <br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Click個play制聽下歌先啦！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" clas